About Us


Horseman Capital Management is an investment company that provides money management expertise to eligible counterparties and professional clients.
Total assets under management are over USD 1.1bn as at 30th June 2017.



Founded by John Horseman in July 2000 the company provides money management expertise covering various equity strategies. We are owned entirely by the founding partners and directors and the firm is run by a small team of talented and experienced professionals.Our offices are situated in London (Belgravia) and Jersey with our administration services outsourced to expert service providers.
Horseman Capital Management Limited is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) in the UK. Horseman Capital Management (Jersey) No1 Limited is regulated by the Jersey Financial Services Commission (JFSC).


















